Required Libraries:

Run the following command to install the required libraries:


#sudo wget http://files.f-prot.com/files/unix-trial/fp-Linux.x86.32-ws.tar.gz
#sudo tar -xzvf fp-Linux.x86.32-ws.tar.gz
#cd f-prot
#sudo echo y | sudo ./install-f-prot.pl


Debian:
#sudo apt-get update 
#sudo apt-get install -y nano python make gcc autoconf libtool python-dev libpcre3-dev clamav
#sudo freshclam



RedHat, Fedora:
#sudo yum install -y nano python make gcc automake libtool python-dev libpcre3-dev clamav
#sudo freshclam


